#: ../../../source/docs/porting/simd.rst:1258
msgid ""
"❌ the underlying NEON instruction is not exposed by the Wasm SIMD "
"specification, so it must be emulated via a slow path, e.g. a sequence of "
"several slower SIMD instructions, or a scalar implementation."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../source/docs/porting/simd.rst:1259
msgid ""
"⚫ the given NEON intrinsic is not available. Referencing the intrinsic will "
"cause a compiler error."
msgstr ""

